      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so you're saying the instability in Defendant B's background actually makes him a higher risk for recidivism? walk me through that logic a bit more—why does his housing/work situation necessarily mean he's more likely to re-offend compared to someone from a stable environment?",
